  TITLE     Discovery of parallel pathways of kanamycin biosynthesis allows antibiotic manipulation.
  JOURNAL   Nat. Chem. Biol. 7 (2011) 843-52.
  ORGANISM  Streptomyces kanamyceticus
  SEQUENCE  [up:Q65CC1]
PATHWAY     ec00524  Butirosin and neomycin biosynthesis
            ec01110  Biosynthesis of secondary metabolites
ORTHOLOGY   K13550  2-deoxystreptamine N-acetyl-D-glucosaminyltransferase / 2-deoxystreptamine glucosyltransferase
